                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-191-off1010 t18310630-191-cd1011"></join>, and stealing 1 watch, value 30s., and 3 silver spoons, value 5s., his property; 4 half-crowns, 5 shillings, and 1 sixpence
            </rs>, the monies of 
               
                  <persName id="t18310630-191-victim1426" type="victimName">
